{"name": "odoo12-addon-l10n-it-asset-history-import", "metadata": {"name": "odoo12-addon-l10n-it-asset-history-import", "version": "12.0.1.0.0.99.dev13", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 12.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo12-addon-assets-management", "odoo", "xlrd", "xlsxwriter"], "summary": "Cespiti: importazione storico dati", "upload_time": 1717737656}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fl10n--italy-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/l10n-italy\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/tree/12.0/l10n_it_asset_history_import\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/l10n-italy-12-0/l10n-italy-12-0-l10n_it_asset_history_import\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/l10n-italy&target_branch=12.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# ITA - Gestione cespiti - Importazione storico\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:22b4b7e5972ac541b3308bcd4542b70812ddc23ee8a770a11eadb52ad1e7f198\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\n**\\*Italiano\\***\n\nQuesto modulo permette l'importazione dello storico dei cespiti.\n\n**\\*English\\***\n\nThis module allows to import assets history.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Usage\n\n**Italiano**\n\nCespiti > Gestione cespiti > Importa storico cespiti\nCaricare un file come da istruzioni (nella procedura guidata \u00e8 possibile trovare il modello da utilizzare per l'importazione), es.:\n\n!\\[alt text\\](../static/asset_import.png)\n\n**English**\n\nAssets > Assets Management > Assets History Import\nUpload a file as per instructions (you can find a template to use for import on wizard), e.g.:\n\n!\\[alt text\\](../static/asset_import.png)\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/issues/new?body=module:%20l10n_it_asset_history_import%0Aversion:%2012.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Openforce\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/l10n-italy](https://github.com/OCA/l10n-italy/tree/12.0/l10n_it_asset_history_import) project